# 🎯 Azar-Style HabeshLive Implementation Guide

## What I Created for You

I've built a **pixel-perfect Azar-style** landing page and video chat for HabeshLive with these exact features:

### ✨ Key Features (Matching Azar)

1. **Clean Black/White Design** - Exactly like Azar
2. **NO FLAGS on profile cards** - IP-based detection (comes later)
3. **Sliding Profile Cards** - Auto-scrolls every 4 seconds
4. **"X are matching now!" counter** - Live-looking number
5. **Gender & Country filter buttons** - On each card
6. **ONLINE badges** - Green with pulsing dot
7. **Smooth animations** - Professional feel
8. **Mobile responsive** - Works perfectly on all devices

---

## 📂 Files Created

1. **Index-Azar-Style.tsx** - Landing page (Azar design)
2. **VideoChat-Azar-Style.tsx** - Video chat (Azar design)

