## 🎨 Design Breakdown

### Landing Page Features:

**Header:**
```
habeshalive                [Log in]
```
- Simple logo (lowercase, like Azar)
- White "Log in" button (rounded)

**Live Counter:**
```
● 18,542 are matching now!
```
- Green pulsing dot
- Big number
- Gray text

**Profile Cards (2x2 Grid):**
```
┌─────────────────┐  ┌─────────────────┐
│ ● ONLINE        │  │ ● ONLINE        │
│                 │  │                 │
│   [Photo]       │  │   [Photo]       │
│                 │  │                 │
│ Sara, 24        │  │ Daniel, 26      │
│      [Gender ▼] │  │     [Country ▼] │
└─────────────────┘  └─────────────────┘
```
- Auto-slides every 4 seconds
- Smooth transitions
- ONLINE badge top-left
- Name/age bottom-left
- Filter button bottom-right
- NO FLAGS (IP-based later)

**CTA Button:**
```
[▶ Start Video Chat]
```
- Big white button
- Video icon
- Rounded corners

**Content:**
- "HabeshLive Video Chat & Talk to Strangers"
- "Connect with Habesha Worldwide!"
- Features section (3 cards)
- FAQs (accordion)
- Footer (clean, minimal)

---

### Video Chat Features:

**Three States:**

1. **Ready State:**
```
      [Camera Icon]
   Ready to Connect?
Meet Habesha people worldwide
   [Start Matching]
```

2. **Searching State:**
```
      [Spinning Loader]
Finding someone for you...
Connecting with Habesha community
```

3. **Connected State:**
```
┌──────────────────────┐  ┌──────────┐
│ ● ONLINE            │  │   You    │
│ Sara, 24            │  │          │
│ Los Angeles, USA    │  │ [Your    │
│                     │  │  Video]  │
│  [Partner Video]    │  │          │
│            [Report] │  │          │
└──────────────────────┘  └──────────┘
```

**Control Bar:**
```
[📷] [🎤] [🔊] | [💬] [⏭] [❌]
```
- Camera on/off
- Mic on/off
- Speaker on/off
- Chat toggle
- Skip to next
- End call

