## 🔧 Implementation Steps

### Step 1: Replace Your Files

```bash
# Your project structure
habeshalive/
├── src/
│   └── pages/
│       ├── Index.tsx       ← Replace with Index-Azar-Style.tsx
│       └── VideoChat.tsx   ← Replace with VideoChat-Azar-Style.tsx
```

### Step 2: Test the Features

**Landing Page:**
- [ ] Profile cards slide automatically
- [ ] "Log in" button visible
- [ ] Live counter shows
- [ ] Filter buttons on cards
- [ ] "Start Video Chat" button works

**Video Chat:**
- [ ] "Start Matching" shows loader
- [ ] Connects after 2.5 seconds
- [ ] Shows partner info (no flags yet)
- [ ] Camera toggle works
- [ ] Mic toggle works
- [ ] Chat opens/closes
- [ ] Skip finds new partner
- [ ] End Call returns to ready

