## 📱 IP-Based Flag System (Coming Later)

**How it will work:**

1. User visits site
2. Backend detects IP address
3. Returns country flag
4. Shows flag on their profile card

**For now:**
- Cards show NO flags
- Just name, age, city
- Filter buttons work (placeholder)

**When you add backend:**
```javascript
// Get user's country from IP
const userCountry = await fetch('/api/ip-lookup');
// Show appropriate flag
const flagEmoji = countryToFlag(userCountry);
```

