## 🎨 Color Scheme (Azar Style)

```css
Background: #181818 (dark gray)
Cards: #1a1a1a (slightly lighter)
Borders: #2a2a2a (subtle)
Text: #ffffff (white)
Secondary: #999999 (gray)
Accent: #ffffff (white buttons)
Green: #00c853 (online status)
```

