## 🚀 Next Steps

### Phase 1: Current (Azar UI) ✅
- Beautiful Azar-style design
- Working buttons
- Sliding cards
- No flags yet

### Phase 2: Add Backend
```javascript
// IP detection
app.get('/api/ip-lookup', async (req, res) => {
  const ip = req.ip;
  const country = await ipLookup(ip);
  res.json({ country, flag: countryToFlag(country) });
});
```

### Phase 3: Add Real Photos
- Upload real Habesha user photos
- Replace Unsplash placeholders
- Add moderation system

### Phase 4: Add Matching Logic
- Gender filter
- Country filter
